title: 284: DJ's Top 50 3.0, WWE's Jim Ross on Baker Mayfield
itunes:title: 284: DJ's Top 50 3.0, WWE's Jim Ross on Baker Mayfield
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dive into the Rams/Patriots trade (1:01) and throw out bold predictions ahead of the 2018 NFL Draft (12:56). DJ then updates his top 50 prospects list before they preview the offensive line class (24:19). The guys wrap the show by interviewing WWE Hall of Fame announcer and Oklahoma super fan Jim Ross to chat about his friend Baker Mayfield and scouting football players to professional wrestlers (29:17). Check the full interview out on the Baker Mayfield 360 episode next week.
